th is targeted through direct sales in aviation, maritime, and land mobility.\n\n### **Summary**\nThe excerpts indicate that SpaceX has made massive cumulative investments in the Starlink constellation, deploying thousands of satellites to achieve significant scale (10.3M subscribers, $11.4B annual revenue by 2025). While current capital expenditures run in the billions annually, a further step-change is planned with the deployment of higher-capacity V3 satellites on Starship and a **$19.6 billion commitment** to acquire strategic spectrum, signaling continued heavy investment to capitalize on a vast remaining market opportunity.',
